"AI is changing the game and you're being left behind..."


...is what I would say if I were fear mongering.

The reality is that AI is here, and it is genuinely useful. Even if you are not interested in vibe coding, staying informed is becoming increasingly important.

That is why I have been completing courses on Anthropic Academy, built by the team at the frontier of modern generative AI development.

